snippet.title: Forge Your Legacy in Life is Feudal: MMO
snippet.description:
Welcome to The Realm, the world of Life is Feudal: MMO. Here, brave souls work the earth, forge weapons and fight to the death over the course of their epic feudal journeys. Are you ready to join The Realm?

https://play.lifeisfeudal.com/
